columnConfigurations.columnName: FI-AP item cleared early without discount (%)
columnConfigurations.columnAlias: FI-AP item cleared early without discount (%)

dataSource.query:
SELECT
	 event_name AS Variant,
    "Number of Cases",
    "Time until invoice clearing (days)",
    "Time until supplier invoices created and posted (days)",
    "FI-AP item cleared early without discount (%)",
    "Late Payments (%)",
    "FI-AP cleared with discount lost (%)",
    "FI-AP cleared with payment block (%)"
FROM (
	SELECT
    	count(case_id) AS "Number of Cases",
        event_name AS Variant,
        AVG ("4 - Lead time from start - FI-AP items cleared") 
        	AS "Time until invoice clearing (days)", 
        AVG ("4 - Lead time from start - Supplier invoices created and posted") 
        	AS "Time until supplier invoices created and posted (days)",
        AVG ("2 - Blocker - FI-AP items cleared more than 3 days before net due date and with no discount") * 100
        	AS "FI-AP item cleared early without discount (%)",
        AVG ("2 - Blocker - FI-AP items cleared after net due date") * 100 
        	AS "Late Payments (%)",
        AVG ("2 - Blocker - FI-AP items cleared despite payment block") * 100 
        	AS "FI-AP cleared with payment block (%)",
        AVG ("2 - Blocker - FI-AP items cleared with discount lost") * 100 
        	AS "FI-AP cleared with discount lost (%)"
	FROM THIS_PROCESS
	GROUP BY 2
) AS sub
ORDER BY 2 DESC
LIMIT 5
